2. PROTECTION OF FUNCTIONAL LOGIC  (EXPRESSLY EMPHASIZED)
---------------------------------------------------------------

The functional logic of the Software — including but not limited to:

  - the three-tier investment architecture (PRE-MATCH / LIVE / ACCUMULATOR),
  - the multi-source intelligence aggregation methodology and the
    confluence-score calculation (0–6.0 scale across Odds, Football-Data,
    BallDontLie NBA, Reddit, and Telegram sources),
  - the odds drift detection and sharp-money-signal heuristics,
  - the Claude-AI system prompts, analysis framing, tier-aware chat
    behaviors, and VALUE/WATCH/SKIP recommendation markers,
  - the accumulator correlation-detection logic and combined-odds
    calculation,
  - the bet tracking model, P&L analytics, equity-curve construction,
    per-sport breakdown formulas, and filter/search implementation,
  - the Hive schema and local persistence layout,
  - the MonitoredChannel reliability-scoring algorithm (Novo/Niska/
    Srednja/Visoka labels and weighting factors),
  - the combination, orchestration, and interaction of the above,

constitutes original intellectual work of the copyright holder and is
protected as copyrightable expression AND as trade secret / know-how.
Reimplementation of the above logic in a different programming language,
framework, or architecture — with the intent to reproduce the behavior,
capabilities, or competitive advantage of BetSight — is expressly
FORBIDDEN and will be treated as infringement of this license and, where
applicable, as misappropriation of trade secrets.

Reading the source code does NOT grant you the right to reimplement what
you have read.

